	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说，<delay20 />你要是愿意的话，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在来和我<delay8 />玩个小游戏吧～？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你赢了，<delay20 />
我就把<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
当做奖品送给你，<delay20 /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />来不来？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好呀好呀～！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">现在稍微有点不方便……</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好呀～<delay20 />那就来玩吧！<delay40 />
